
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <!-- bootstrap -->
        <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-T3c6CoIi6uLrA9TneNEoa7RxnatzjcDSCmG1MXxSR1GAsXEV/Dwwykc2MPK8M2HN" crossorigin="anonymous">
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-C6RzsynM9kWDrMNeT87bh95OGNyZPhcTNXj1NW7RuBCsyN/o0jlpcV8Qyq46cDfL" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
        <!-- jquery -->
        <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.7.1.js" integrity="sha256-eKhayi8LEQwp4NKxN+CfCh+3qOVUtJn3QNZ0TciWLP4=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

        <title>공구카</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="container">
            <br>
            <h3>차량등록 화면입니다!</h3>
            <p>차량등록에 필요한 정보를 입력해주세요</p>

            <form action="/chaincode/registercar" method="post">
                <label class="form-label">차량이름 : </label>
                <input class="form-control" type="text" name="carname">
                <br>
                <label class="form-label">차량색상 : </label>
                <select class="form-select" name="carcolor">
                    <option value="RED">빨강</option>
                    <option value="BLUE">파랑</option>
                    <option value="BLACK">검정</option>
                    <option value="HOTPINK">진분홍</option>
                </select>
                <br>    
                <label class="form-label">차량가격 : </label>
                <input class="form-control" type="text" name="carprice">
                <br>                       
                <input type="submit" class="btn btn-warning" value="차량등록하기">
            </form>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>